data.description: BEAUTIFUL 2 LEVEL HOME & FULLY FINISHED BASEMENT.  REFINISHED WOOD FLOORS W/EXQUISITE ATTENTION TO DETAIL.  NEW PAINT & LEVOLOR/WOOD BLINDS THROUGHOUT, FORMAL LIVING ROOM FEATURES GAS FIREPLACE, EAT IN KITCHEN WITH NEW PORCELAIN TILE & PANTRY OPENS TO BACKYARD RETREAT AND DECK.  A SPACIOUS MASTER BEDROOM WITH WALK-IN CLOSET, FULL MASTER BATH AND CEILING FAN.  THERE ARE 2 ADDITIONAL BEDROOMS, LAUNDRY AND FULL BATH ON THE UPPER LEVEL.  THE FINISHED BASEMENT OFFERS ADDITIONAL BEDROOM & 3/4 BATH. CENTRAL AIR, SPRINKLER SYSTEM Move-in ready on a quiet street.  Family room in the basement may also be used as an office or noncomforming bedroom without a closet.   Big backyard, perfect for a growing family.  For more photos and information, watch the virtural tour.  Short walk to Cottonwood Creek Park and YMCA Recreation Center featuring an indoor pool, walking and running paths, soccer fields, softball fields, tennis courts, children's play area, sledding, in-line hockey court and more.
